{"article_id":"Onos5xFD1R14lnmY","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"With the Russia investigation over ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"there 's a new conflict","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"consuming Washington :","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Attorney General William Barr versus special counsel Robert Mueller .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"The tension between the two men","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"-- Barr , the public face of the Justice Department , and Mueller , an outwardly silent figure","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"who 's spoken publicly only through written documents --","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"has been building for weeks","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and was on full display Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"as the attorney general testified in the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Barr 's final two minutes of testimony before the Judiciary Committee prompted him to call Mueller 's March 27 letter","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"criticizing Barr 's release of a four-page summary of the special counsel 's report","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"`` a bit snitty . ''","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"At other points of his testimony , Barr undercut the special counsel 's team of prosecutors","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and rejected Mueller 's decisions and reasoning .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"`` I think","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"it was probably written by one of his staff people , ''","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Barr said about the March 27 letter .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Separately ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"when Barr was asked","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"if Mueller 's team of prosecutors were `` the best and the brightest , ''","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"the attorney general responded ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"`` Not necessarily . ''","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Special counsel office spokesman Peter Carr declined to comment on who wrote the March 27 letter ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"which was signed by Mueller ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"or to respond to Barr 's gripes .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"In addition to the fight over Barr 's rollout of the report , Barr and Mueller have also diverged on their legal approaches ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"especially related to the obstruction of justice investigation into President Donald Trump .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Barr 's testimony Wednesday made that even clearer .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Barr dinged Mueller on Wednesday for three of his prosecutorial choices :","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"That Mueller did n't make a decision on obstruction ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that Mueller continued to investigate obstruction","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"and that Mueller rejected the Trump personal attorneys ' legal reasoning on an obstruction case .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"`` We were frankly surprised","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"that they were not going to reach a decision on obstruction , ''","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Barr testified .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"`` We did not understand exactly why the special counsel was not reaching a decision ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"when we pressed him on it ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"he said","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"that his team was still formulating the explanation . '","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"' It was the `` very purpose","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"-- the function","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"he was carrying out , ''","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Barr added .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Barr leaned into an argument","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"he had made to the Justice Department in writing","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"before he became attorney general :","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that the President should n't be investigated for obstruction .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"he disagreed with Mueller 's work in a broader sense .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"`` I think","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"if he felt","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"he should n't go down the path","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"of making a traditional prosecutive decision ,","depth":15},{"id":57,"text":"then he should n't have investigated , ''","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"Barr said .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` That was the time","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"to pull up . ''","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Yet Mueller describes in the report his reasoning","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"for investigating Trump","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"-- and continuing to investigate him .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"The obstruction investigation was n't merely a political distraction ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Mueller says ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"and the special counsel sought to preserve what happened","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"while `` memories were fresh","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"and documentary materials were available , ''","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"according to the report .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Mueller reasoned","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"even if a president can not be prosecuted while in office ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"he or she can still commit crimes ,","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"a prosecution could come later ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"once the President has left office ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"or Congress may consider the findings .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Half of Mueller 's report examines the President 's actions on 10 topics and how those actions could become part of an obstruction of justice case .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Mueller devotes a significant part of his report","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"analyzing Trump 's actions against a legal standard","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"to bring a case to court .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Several times , Mueller describes how Trump 's intended actions could have obstructed the investigation .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"`` The difference is I used the proper standard , ''","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"Barr said about his decision","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"not to prosecute Trump on obstruction .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Barr also took issue with Mueller 's reaction to the President 's personal legal team .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"The Trump lawyers had argued to Mueller","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that the head of the executive branch could n't obstruct an investigation .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Yet Mueller rejected that .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Barr , instead , highlighted how the President has `` constitutional authorities","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"to supervise proceedings . ''","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"`` The President could terminate that proceeding ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and it would not be a corrupt intent ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"if it was based on false allegations , ''","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"Barr said .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Finally , Barr and Mueller appear to have an even deeper divide over what Mueller 's report says .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Barr downplayed on Wednesday the evidence","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Mueller collected","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"over how the President attempted to obstruct justice ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"particularly when he told then-White House counsel Don McGahn to remove Mueller .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Mueller dismissed the President 's concerns over conflicts of interest as an excuse","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"when he looked at Trump 's orders to McGahn .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Yet Barr focused on the conflicts issue as a reasonable explanation for what Trump did .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"Nadler :","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"Barr wo n't testify","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"because he is terrified","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"Nadler :","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Barr wo n't testify","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"because he is terrified","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"01:22","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"Barr released his four-page summary of the Mueller report on March 24 .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"Mueller then memorialized in two letters to Barr his reactions on March 25 and March 27 .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"Only the March 27 letter has been publicly released ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"but it references the first letter as well .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"In the March 27 letter ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"released Wednesday morning just before the hearing ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Mueller told Barr","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"he `` did not fully capture the context , nature , and substance of this Office 's work and conclusion . ''","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"He urged Barr to release more information to the public immediately ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"and accused the attorney general of undermining the public 's confidence .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"They spoke on the phone the next day , March 28 .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"The Justice Department has described that chat as `` cordial , ''","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"nodding to previous descriptions of the two men 's 30-year friendship .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Others were in the room ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"Barr testified ,","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"and heard the call over speakerphone .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"In testifying about the call ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Barr said","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Mueller 's complaint was more about media coverage of his summary","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"-- yet Mueller 's letter clearly took issue with what Barr wrote to Congress .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"As senators pressed Barr on his approach","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"of blaming the media ,","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"he moved more toward criticizing Mueller and his team .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"`` I said ,","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"Bob ,","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"what 's with the letter ?","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"You know .","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"Why do n't you just pick up the phone","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"and call me","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"if there is an issue ? ''","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"Barr told senators about the call .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Yet Mueller did not appear at the press conference","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Barr held on April","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"18 hours before the Justice Department released a redacted version of the 448-page Mueller report","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"By then , the President had spent almost a month","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"claiming","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"he was fully exonerated .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"At that press conference , Barr said","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"he and Mueller `` disagreed with some of the special counsel 's legal theories , ''","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"but that generally Mueller had left the decision","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"on charging the President to the attorney general ,","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"and that Barr and Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein decided","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"Trump should n't be charged .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"Barr on Wednesday pointed to Mueller for the delay in the public release of the report .","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"He and Mueller discussed redacting confidential information from the grand jury in the report early in March ,","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"but","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"when Mueller handed the report to him ,","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"`` unfortunately it did not come in that form . ''","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"Mueller , for his part , is n't yet scheduled to testify ,","depth":5},{"id":164,"text":"though several members of Congress have said","depth":6},{"id":165,"text":"he must .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":331,"left":0,"right":330,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":330,"left":268,"right":329,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":191,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":175,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":169,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":1,"right":168,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":168,"left":167,"right":4,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":167,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":172,"right":173,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":172,"left":171,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":171,"left":5,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":187,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":179,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":177,"right":178,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":176,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":176,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":186,"left":181,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":180,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"p